</taxonomicName>
Hampson, 1913. Catalogue of 
<taxonomicName id="34F8DF31AE63F22152177DAEE95C7F13" authorityName="Dognin" authorityYear="1891" class="Insecta" family="Pantheidae" genus="Gaujonia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="71" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="order">Lepidoptera</taxonomicName>
